  <note reference-line="7" id="3">
    <original>udriyati (sī. syā.)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet>Nimittakammaṃ nāma nimittaṃ karoti – ‘‘iminā dussena kathinaṃ attharissāmī’’ti. Parikathā nāma parikathaṃ karoti – ‘‘imāya parikathāya kathinadussaṃ nibbattessāmī’’ti. Kukkukataṃ nāma anādiyadānaṃ vuccati. Sannidhi nāma dve sannidhiyo – karaṇasannidhi vā nicayasannidhi vā. Nissaggiyaṃ nāma kayiramāne aruṇaṃ uṭṭhahati </snippet>
    <match>uṭṭhahati</match>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="sī." source="sri lanka">udriyati</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="syā." source="thai">udriyati</alternative>
    </alternatives>
  </note>
